<br>
From the gnome's perspective, I'd have to say apathy is the rule.  We care about gnomish things and our tinkered contraptions for the most part.  Most of the other races don't see us as a threat, so they let us in their towns.  The choices you make in your journeys will always effect how certain factions will treat you.<br>
<br>
